      <description>Let's talk about the Making Memories SLICE Spring Design Card.  What do you love most about springtime?  Is it fresh juicy strawberries from the garden?  How about dressing up in your Sunday best to attend Easter service, followed up with watching the kids hunt for eggs?  Or maybe you just love rain showers, seeing the [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/making-memories-slice/Making_Memories_SLICE-Making_Memories_SLICE_Spring_Design_Card.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Let's talk about the <strong>Making Memories SLICE Spring Design Card</strong>.  What do you love most about springtime?  Is it fresh juicy strawberries from the garden?  How about dressing up in your Sunday best to attend Easter service, followed up with watching the kids hunt for eggs?  Or maybe you just love rain showers, seeing the flowers bloom, or the birds return to your yard.</p>
<p>No matter what you love best about this time of year, this design card from Making Memories most likely has it covered.  Use it to make die cuts for your scrapbook layouts, handmade cards, and other paper crafts.  You can make cutouts from one to four inches in size, in half inch increments.</p>
<p>You can say anything in style with the pretty font that is contained in this cartridge.  Both capitalized and lowercase letters are included, as well as numbers and typographical symbols</p>
<p>There are several phrases on the SLICE Spring design card, including:<br />
Blossom, Egg, daisy, Plant, fresh, Hunt, laugh, spring, Easter, Grow, flower, new, spring fever, garden, Lily, beauty, and Rainy.</p>
<p>You can also use it to make die cut shapes of the following:</p>
<p>Gardening Tools - watering cans, shovels, wheelbarrows and rakes<br />
Insects and Critters - bunnies, chicks, frogs, ducks, squirrels, caterpillars, ants, butterflies, birds, and deer<br />
Fruits and Veggies - strawberries, cherries and carrots<br />
Easter - Easter eggs and baskets, fresh grass and bows<br />
Other - umbrellas and rain boots, kites, clover, tags, and more</p>
<p>As you can see, the <a href="http://www.diecutfun.com/slice-design-cards/">SLICE Spring Design Card</a> can make die cut shapes for all those special springtime moments!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-236" style="border: 1px solid black;" title="Making Memories Slice Spring Design Card" src="http://www.diecutfun.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/slice-spring-design-card.gif" alt="Making Memories Slice Spring Design Card" width="300" height="300" /></p>
<p>&lt;&lt;&lt; Return to Die Cut Fun's home page for more information about the <a href="http://www.diecutfun.com/">Making Memories SLICE</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.diecutfun.com/slice-design-cards/spring/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
