      <description>What a clever idea!  The Making Memories Slice Calendar design card can literally make an entire year's worth of die cuts.  This cartridge, new for summer 2009, is perfect for creating handmade wall calendars and datebooks which by the way, make thoughtful gifts.  However, don't stop there!  It's also ideal for use in your other [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/making-memories-slice/Making_Memories_SLICE-Making_Memories_SLICE_Calendar_Design_Card.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>What a clever idea!  The <strong>Making Memories Slice Calendar design card</strong> can literally make an entire year's worth of die cuts.  This cartridge, new for summer 2009, is perfect for creating handmade wall calendars and datebooks which by the way, make thoughtful gifts.  However, don't stop there!  It's also ideal for use in your other paper crafting endeavors, including scrapbook layouts and more.</p>
<p>This design card, like many of the others, includes an upper and lowercase font, numbers, and typographical symbols.</p>
<p>It also has plenty of words and phrases, including the twelve months, the days of the week, holidays, and important events, such as "birthday", "anniversary", and "vacation".</p>
<p>There are plenty of shapes too, including holiday-specific ones such as fireworks and jack o' lanterns, weather-related cutouts, including umbrellas and snowflakes, and the twelve zodiac symbols.</p>
<p>The <a href="http://www.diecutfun.com/slice-design-cards/">SLICE Calendar design card</a> will give you the capability to make die cuts ranging in size from one to four inches.  It's a versatile cartridge that is sure to be used again and again!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-228" style="border: 1px solid black;" title="SLICE Calendar Design Card" src="http://www.diecutfun.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/slice-calendar-design-card.jpg" alt="SLICE Calendar Design Card" width="300" height="300" /></p>
<p>&lt;&lt;&lt;Return to DieCutFun.com to learn more about the <a href="http://www.diecutfun.com/">Making Memories SLICE</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
