      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.diecutfun.com/?page_id=221</guid>
      <description>The Making Memories SLICE Sports design card will give you more than one reason to cheer!  Whether your favorite athlete is first learning how to swing a bat with her Little League teammates, or recently led his high school football team to a state victory, the die cuts you can make with this cartridge are [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/making-memories-slice/Making_Memories_SLICE-Making_Memories_SLICE_Sports_Design_Card.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The <strong>Making Memories SLICE Sports design card</strong> will give you more than one reason to cheer!  Whether your favorite athlete is first learning how to swing a bat with her Little League teammates, or recently led his high school football team to a state victory, the die cuts you can make with this cartridge are just the thing you need for your scrapbook pages.  You can also use it to make handmade thank you cards for coaches and team parents, as well as invitations to tailgating and Super Bowl parties.</p>
<p>With this design card, you can make sports-inspired die cuts in seven different sizes, ranging from one inch to four inches in size.  Letters, numbers, words and phrases, silhouettes, and other shapes are included.</p>
<p>First, let's talk about the font on this design card.  Varsity style lower and uppercase letters and numbers are included.  They are reminiscent of the numbers and letters you see on high school letter jackets.</p>
<p>There are also several phrases - "Goal!", "TOUCHDOWN", and "Go Fight Win!" are a few examples of the phrases that you will find on this design cartridge.</p>
<p>More than thirty action-packed silhouette shapes are included, representing a wide variety of different sporting activities.  The traditional ones that you would expect to find are present, including baseball, basketball, football, and soccer.  However, there are also silhouette shapes of bicyclists, golfers, snowboarders, skiers, cheerleaders, dancers, and more.</p>
<p>That's not all!  The <a href="http://www.diecutfun.com/slice-design-cards/">SLICE Sports Design Card</a> has a good selection of sporting equipment, including balls, cleats, helmets, trophies, flags, stopwatches, and score boards.</p>
<p>As you can see, this is one that you will definitely want to add to your collection.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="size-full wp-image-222 aligncenter" style="border: 1px solid black;" title="SLICE Sports Design Card" src="http://www.diecutfun.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/slice-sports-design-card.gif" alt="SLICE Sports Design Card" width="300" height="300" /></p>
<p>&lt;&lt;&lt;You're on a roll!  Return to our home page to learn more about the <a href="http://www.diecutfun.com/">Making Memories SLICE</a>...</p>
]]></content:encoded>
